"\\quad x_{ij} \\leq y_j,\\,\\textrm{ for }\\,  i = 1,\\ldots, n; \\, j = 1,\\ldots, n,\n"
"\\quad x_{jj} = y_j,\\,\\textrm{ for }\\,  j = 1,\\ldots, n,"
