msgstr "\\sum_{i=1}^n \\sum_{j=1}^n \\rho_{ij} x_{ij} = [\\rho_{11},\\rho_{12},\\ldots,\\rho_{11}, \\rho_{22},\\ldots,\\rho_{nn}|{\\bf 0}_n ]{\\bf z} =: {\\bf c}_0^T {\\bf z}"

